data.description: LINCOLN SQUARE/ BUDLONG WOODS desirable location!Bright and Spacious 2nd-floor condo. The spacious 2-bedroom unit also includes 1/4 of a space in the basement with a washer and dryer. It could be used for a workout/hobby space or storage area.  The primary bedroom is 29x11 with its own setting area. The unit is perfectly located close to public transportation, grocery on Lincoln, shopping, Swedish Covenant Hospital, and Galter Lifecenter, as well as great restaurants boutiques, and salons in Lincoln Square.
